CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Mechanics Bank is an independent, full-service bank based in Walnut Creek, California, with over $16 billion in assets, a best-in-class deposit franchise and 111 branches. Founded in 1905 to help families, businesses and communities prosper, the historic financial institution has grown to become one of the largest California-based banks.
